      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 35,
      "text": "Phase Kickback — The Heart of QPE",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 55,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "How a phase on the target qubit 'kicks back' to the control qubit",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#666",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "section1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 45,
      "text": "1. Setup: Control in superposition, Target is eigenstate |ψ⟩ of U\n   H|0⟩ = (|0⟩ + |1⟩)/√2    and    U|ψ⟩ = e²ᵖⁱᶿ|ψ⟩",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#37474f",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3f2fd",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "c-q0-line",
      "type": "line",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1976d2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "points": [[0,0],[300,0]]
    },
